#: src-en/data/events_special_lightspeed.xml.append:25
msgid ""
"data/events_special_lightspeed.xml.append$//event[@name=\"LIGHTSPEED_SECTOR_WARP_RADIKAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You are about to reroute. Below is the Atlas entry for this sector.\n"
"\tName: RadiKal sector\n"
"\tType: Neutral\n"
"\tDominant Faction: RK Bam, RK Punk, RK Scorch\n"
"\tRebel Threat Level: Very Low\n"
"\tLocations of Interest: Bam HQ, Punk HQ, Scorch HQ\n"
"\t\n"
"\tThe dangerous sector where RadiKal subfactions develop illegal equipment. Specialists from everywhere secretly come to keep up with the tech, regulate its trade or steal it. Mind whatever Radikal (RK) equipment you have in there!\n"
"\t[W.I.P. ! Report any bugs @Dj0z on discord.]"

